%% Diagram: Recovery Sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Eng as On-call\nengineer
    participant Phone as Phone /\nexternal chat
    participant DC as Data center\nbuilding
    participant Sec as Physical\nsecurity
    participant Console as Backbone router\nserial console
    participant BGP as Edge BGP /\nupstream peers
    participant Res as Recursive\nresolvers
    participant App as Meta service\nfleet

    Eng->>Phone: Coordinate via cell + non-FB chat\n(Workplace + wiki are down)
    Eng->>DC: Travel to nearest data center
    DC->>Sec: Activate manual access protocol
    Sec-->>Eng: Override badge reader, escort in
    Eng->>Console: Connect via serial / OOB cart
    Console-->>Eng: Identify + revert maintenance change
    Console->>BGP: Backbone restored\n=> edge health probes pass
    BGP-->>BGP: Re-announce withdrawn prefixes\n(peak ~21:17 UTC)
    BGP-->>Res: Routes re-appear in global table
    Res-->>App: SERVFAIL stops; clients reconnect
    Note over App: Staged ramp using\n"storm" drill playbook\nto avoid thundering-herd
